Key Match Events: Mama Baldé scored for Guinea-Bissau in the 42nd minute.
Mohamed Salah scored for Egypt in the 70th minute.
The match ended in a 1-1 draw.
Nasser Maher replaced Ahmed Amin Aoufa for Egypt in the 90+2 minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place at Stade du 24 Septembre in Bissau, Guinea-Bissau.
The game was part of the 2026 World Cup Qualifying - CAF, Group Stage.
